summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6544 for the improvement of Northeast 103rd Street from approximately 210 feet west of Sand Point Way Northeast to Sand Point Way Northeast; by establishing and seal coating; under Ordinance No. 101133, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
